Title: Relates to the members of the public health and health planning council
Summary: Increases the number of members on the public health and health planning council from twenty-five to twenty-six and requires one member represent hospice care providers.
LawCode: Amd ยง220, Pub Health L
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the public health law, in relation to increasing the number of members on the public health and health planning council
